ready\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md:\n  Line 56: The CLI is invoked as `kubectl-agentcube` with subcommands: `pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status`.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tests/test_cli.py:\n  Line 107:         result = runner.invoke(app, [\"status\", \"--help\"])\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n  Line 119: - Design stage ST-3 complete - implementation ready\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Implementation Ready)\n  Line 152: - Design stage ST-3 completed - ready for implementation\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/picod/tasks.md:\n  Line 9: - **Design Stage**: ST-3 completed\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md:\n  Line 6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 114 matches (14 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":114,"truncated":true},"title":"AR-023|invoke.*status|ST-3","time":{"start":1775863978391,