{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864010944,"sessionID":"ses_286429a63ffemovC7eb4MkAGfC","part":{"id":"prt_d79be1325001Jbuin9EPDnIlrO","messageID":"msg_d79be0660001YPmNnblhVkWa6Q","sessionID":"ses_286429a63ffemovC7eb4MkAGfC","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_5e8f22d74c674f37a7f0f516","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-023 — CLI Invoke/Status Command Tasks\n\n**AR:** AR-023  \n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n\n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: CLI Interface Implementation\n- [ ] **T001** Implement `invoke` command in `agentcube/cli/main.py` with options: `--workspace`, `--payload`, `--header`, `--provider`, `--verbose`\n- [ ] **T002** Implement `status` command in `agentcube/cli/main.py` with options: `--workspace`, `--provider`, `--verbose`\n- [ ] **T003** Add `_handle_error` function for error formatting with verbose mode support\n\n### Phase 2: Runtime Implementation\n- [ ] **T004** Implement `InvokeRuntime` class in `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`\n- [ ] **T005** Implement `_validate_invoke_prerequisites` method in InvokeRuntime (AR-023-004)\n- [ ] **T006** Implement `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube` with session header support (AR-023-005-B)\n- [ ] **T007** Implement URL rewrite for AgentRuntime CR deployments (AR-023-005-C)\n- [ ] **T008** Implement `_direct_http_invocation` for k8s provider (AR-023-006)\n- [ ] **T009** Implement `StatusRuntime` class in `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`\n- [ ] **T010** Implement `_get_cr_k8s_status` for AgentCube provider (AR-023-011)\n- [ ] **T011** Implement `_get_k8s_status` for standard k8s provider (AR-023-012)\n\n### Phase 3: Provider Integration\n- [ ] **T012** Add `get_agent_status` method to `KubernetesProvider` (AR-023-012-A)\n- [ ] **T013** Add `get_agent_runtime` method to `AgentCubeProvider` (AR-023-011)\n\n### Phase 4: Input Validation\n- [ ] **T014** Validate workspace path exists (AR-023-004-A)\n- [ ] **T015** Validate metadata file exists (AR-023-004-B)\n- [ ] **T016** Validate agent is published before invoke (AR-023-004-C)\n- [ ] **T017** Validate JSON payload parsing (AR-023-002-A/B/C)\n- [ ] **T018** Validate header format with colon split (AR-023-003-A/B/C/D)\n\n### Phase 5: HTTP Request/Response\n- [ ] **T019** Send POST request with JSON body (AR-023-007-A)\n- [ ] **T020** Handle success response (2xx) (AR-023-007-B)\n- [ ] **T021** Handle HTTP error response (4xx/5xx) (AR-023-007-C)\n\n### Phase 6: Output Display\n- [ ] **T022** Display status in Rich Table format (AR-023-013-A)\n- [ ] **T023** Return appropriate exit codes for errors (AR-023-013-B)\n\n### Phase 7: Testing\n- [ ] **T024** Write unit tests for `InvokeRuntime.invoke()` with valid payload\n- [ ] **T025** Write unit tests for `InvokeRuntime.invoke()` with invalid JSON payload\n- [ ] **T026** Write unit tests for header parsing (AR-023-003-A/B/C/D)\n- [ ] **T027** Write unit tests for `StatusRuntime.get_status()` with agentcube provider\n- [ ] **T028** Write unit tests for `StatusRuntime.get_status()` with k8s provider\n- [ ] **T029** Write unit tests for not-published scenario (AR-023-010-A)\n- [ ] **T030** Add CLI integration tests for `invoke` command using CliRunner\n- [ ] **T031** Add CLI integration tests for `status` command using CliRunner\n\n### Phase 8: Documentation\n- [ ] **T032** Document CLI usage for invoke command\n- [ ] **T033** Document CLI usage for status command\n\n## Verification Criteria\n\n- [ ] **VC001** `kubectl-agentcube invoke --help` shows all required options\n- [ ] **VC002** `kubectl-agentcube status --help` shows all required options\n- [ ] **VC003** Invoke returns exit code 1 for invalid JSON payload\n- [ ] **VC004** Invoke returns exit code 1 for invalid header format\n- [ ] **VC005** Invoke adds X-Agentcube-Session-Id header when session_id exists\n- [ ] **VC006** Invoke returns exit code 1 when agent not published\n- [ ] **VC007** Status returns \"not_published\" and exit code 1 when agent not published\n- [ ] **VC008** Status displays Rich Table with agent info\n- [ ] **VC009** All unit tests pass\n- [ ] **VC010** CLI integration tests pass","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775864010931,"end":1775864010941}}}}
